<p>My code only plays the audio when the ImageView is released. What should I add in order to make the audio start as soon as it is pressed?</p>  <pre><code>MediaPlayer mp = null;  public void next (View view) {     if (mp != null) {         mp.stop();         mp.release();     }     mp = MediaPlayer.create(this, R.raw.dry);     mp.start(); } </code></pre>  <p>XML code:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;ImageView     android:layout_width="match_parent"     android:layout_height="match_parent"     android:src="@drawable/seethrough"     android:clickable="true"     android:id="@+id/Seethrough"     android:onClick="next"     /&gt; </code></pre>